Name = \fBname()\fR\&
.br
Func = \fBdbg_fun()\fR\&
.br
Timeout = timeout()
.br
Void = term()
.br
.RE
.RS
.LP
Removes a previously installed debug function from the process\&. \fIFunc\fR\& must be the same as previously installed\&.
